      "comment_id" : 106450366,
      "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
      "body" : "Yes, unpacking multiple jars has some important drawbacks. Another one is the issue with META-INF files like signature files or SPI (services/package.Class) files which are overwritten by assembly plugin by default. Shade plugin has some special transformers which can merge the files if needed"
    } ],
