    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>In the case of an executable jar, another way to think about a fat jar is one you can execute by invoking:</p>\n\n<pre><code>java -jar myFatLibrary.jar\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>without the need for <code>-cp</code> / <code>--classpath</code>, or even double clicking the jar icon.</p>\n"
